<img class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-40 group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-1000" data-alt="serene yoga practitioner in a dark minimalist studio with soft purple and teal ambient light coming from the floor" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDNgkJ-ZnML0PT9MQ4WL9C9weuozYPLDBD79VCMCNDDoTLKRONiKALavM-W91pj7nkwLQhbw16gLIjw0QBYsxBRp3LYPfLfB8T1TJIxZIqXKIbdMVHEFEl8NLi4Jc4KN-cNEcmZurgfj2BOSJWcv9YuFuiWIeiMavw-sDZ28CA0P5KUzI-Bb2tyRZuOG6bjUHcCJZZWiatvGLPTWePU3fSEgg438q35YpbMG5O3EVYFXtuO2TP9MaB-aGg7VNYvIm8ZbJSDAMXfm58"/>
<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-background via-transparent to-transparent"></div>
<div class="absolute bottom-8 left-8 max-w-lg">
<h3 class="text-3xl font-black mb-2">The Ritual of Wellness</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant">BMI is just one metric in your expansive health portfolio. Use our tools to build a comprehensive picture of your daily performance.</p>
</div>
</div>
